videos.description: NC State's Abdul-Malik Abu goes right down the lane and throws down the vicious jam over a pair of Florida State defenders for the hoop and the harm.
videos.headline: Abu leaves Florida State with no chance of stopping him

videos.description: Florida State's Jarquez Smith cleans up the miss with a massive two-handed putback dunk right over a pair of NC State defenders.
videos.headline: Smith goes over two defenders for mega-putback dunk
